sixth.translate: шестой, секста, шестая часть, шестое число
examples: My brother is in sixth grade.
Only about a sixth of the town voted for her.
The sixth grade classroom was a zoo after recess.
The pottery dates back to the sixth century B.C.E.
Agassi was at that time ranked sixth in the world.
the artistic ferment of the late sixth century
Head for 44th Street, a few blocks east of Sixth Avenue.
My regiment was brigaded with the Sixth, Seventh, and Eighth Regiments.
Manchester United will meet Blackburn Rovers in the sixth round of the Cup.
